org.testng

Class SuiteRunner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.testng.SuiteRunner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, IAttributes, IInvokedMethodListener, ISuite, ITestNGListener

    public class SuiteRunner
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISuite, java.io.Serializable, IInvokedMethodListener
    SuiteRunner is responsible for running all the tests included in one suite. The test start is triggered by run() method.
    Author:
    Cedric Beust, Apr 26, 2004
    See Also:
